d Fairchild Camera. Elec\ntrographic Corp. backed down.\nWashington exchange\neo\nPotomac Elec Pwr common\u2014100 at 14.\n20 at 14.\nPotomac Klee Pwr 3.90 pf B'\u201470 at\nMerssrithaler Linotype\u201420 at .51 Vi.\nGarflnckel common\u201419 at 19',.\nPeoples Drug common\u201444 at 33VI.\nWashington Oas com\u2014100 at 29Vi,\nat 26V,\nPUBLIC UTILITY\nBONDS\nBid\nAm TAtTA: cv db 23is 1957 111 Vi\nAm TAT cv deb 2VsS 1001 loft\nCap Transit 1st ref 4a 1094 09\nGeorgetown Gas 1st 5s 1961 114\nPot Elec Pow 3 Vo 1099 109\nPot Elec Pow 3V4s 1977.. 108\nPot Elec POW 3s 1983 __ 101 Vi\nWashington Oas 6a 1960 122Vi\nPUBLIC UTILITY\nSTOCKS.\nAm T At T _ _ 153\nCapital Transit I63,\nN 4 W Steamboat \u00ab14> *108\nPot Elec Power com i 90) |3T,\nPEP 3.60'p pfd \u2022\u2022A\u201d 11.80) 43Vi\nPEP 3.60Vc pf B\" (1.80. 44\nWash Gas Lt com (1.50).. 28\u2018i\nWash Gaa Lt cu pf (4.25)_*102\nWash Os Lt cu cv pf (4.60) .*104 V\nAsked.\n112>/a\n106\n98\n154\n17>,\nin vjis li cu cv ui Iy.OUI. iiw /a J\nBANK AND TRUST COMPANIES.\n14\n45\n45\n2 7 Vi\n103\n107\n29\n40\n27>4\n350\n312\n830\nAmer Sec At Tr New(tl.OO)\nBank of Bethesda (tl.50>..\nCapital 90) _\nCom Savings (tlO)_\nLiberty (8)_\nLincoln <+5) ..._\nNational Sav Tr (8.00)\nPr Georges B At Tr (tl.OO)\nRiggs (121__\nUnion Trust Co (tl.OO)_\nWashington (6) _ _\nWaah Loan 9t Tr (12) _\nFIRE AND TITLE INSURANCE.\nAmerican (rO) _190\nColumbia (t.30)_\nFiremen's (1.40)\nNational Union (.75)\nReal Estate <t6) 190\nMISCELLANEOUS.\nCarpel Corp (2.00) 25\ngarfinckel com (1.50) 19\narfl 6Vicu cv pf (1 875) 24Mi\nGarfl 4Va% eu cv pf (1.125)\n81\n80\n83\n420\nSo\n320\n36\n190\n330\n\u00a33 Vi 18 Vi\nHecht Co (1.60)\n3%r\u00bb cu pf <3.76). _\nHecht\nLanaton Mono (t2.00)\nMergenthaler Lino (a 1.60)\nNatl Mtg At Inv pf (p.45).\n(*1.6'\nPeoples Drug com (*1.60)\nSecurity Storage (t5)\nTer Ref At Wh Corp (3)\nWdwd Atjmth com (t2.00)\n21\n23 Vi\n88 V,\n23 Vg\n61\n8 Vi\n33\n116\ns?\n104\n20\nW'\n25\n91 V,\nW'\n34 Vs\n35\nWdwd At Loth pf new (61\nEk